### 5. API 接口设计

**已有的完整 API（无需新增）：**

```
# 迭代相关
GET    /api/iterations              # 获取迭代列表
GET    /api/iterations/:id          # 获取迭代详情
GET    /api/iterations/current      # 获取当前迭代
POST   /api/iterations              # 创建迭代
PATCH  /api/iterations/:id          # 更新迭代
DELETE /api/iterations/:id          # 删除迭代

# Agent 相关
GET    /api/agents                  # 获取所有 Agent 状态
GET    /api/agents/active          # 获取活跃 Agent
GET    /api/agents/stats/performance # Agent 性能统计
PATCH  /api/agents/progress        # 更新 Agent 进度

# 系统相关
GET    /api/system/overview        # 系统概览
GET    /api/system/metrics         # 系统指标
GET    /api/stats/dashboard        # 完整 Dashboard 统计

# WebSocket
WS     /api/ws                     # WebSocket 连接
```

**WebSocket 事件协议：**

```typescript
// 客户端 → 服务器
{ event: 'subscribe', channel: 'all' }
{ event: 'ping' }

// 服务器 → 客户端
{ event: 'iteration.started', data: {...} }
{ event: 'agent.started', data: {...} }
{ event: 'agent.completed', data: {...} }
{ event: 'system.metrics', data: {...} }
```

---

### 6. 数据流图

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as AutoIterationEngine
    participant D as Dashboard Server
    participant W as WebSocket Service
    participant F as 前端（未来）
    participant DB as Database

    A->>D: initDashboard()
    D-->>A: getServices()

    A->>D: iterationService.create()
    D->>DB: INSERT iteration
    DB-->>D: iteration record
    D-->>A: iteration

    A->>W: broadcast('iteration.started')
    W->>F: WebSocket message
    F-->>W: ack

    A->>W: broadcast('agent.started', agentName)
    W->>F: WebSocket message

    Note over A: Agent 执行中...

    A->>W: broadcast('agent.completed')
    W->>F: WebSocket message

    A->>D: iterationService.update(status: 'completed')
    D->>DB: UPDATE iteration
```

